metadata.name: their easy on the eyes hearts 1/3
metadata.description:
Middle Atlantic ridge 0.0000°N, 20.0000°W.
Mentioned as a general ability of select ancestors, flight could be one or a collective act. The means varied, from levitation to growing wings, to turning into birds, or in the case of the Igbo Landing drownings, allegorized as walking on water to Africa.
